  "content": {
    "prompt": "Construct a function which takes a base and a non-negative exponent as parameters and calculates the base raised to the power of the exponent without using multiplication.",
    "source_code": "def power(base, exp):\n    if exp == 0:\n        return 1\n\n    result = base\n    temp = base\n\n    for i in range(1, exp):\n        for j in range(1, base):\n            result += temp\n        temp = result\n    return result\n\n"
  },
